    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs well, but it will likely need a new set of tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at an affordable price point.",
